TailWord Bot – Terms of Service

Last Updated: 6 February 2026

These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern the use of the TailWord Discord Bot ("TailWord", "the Bot", "Service") operated by the developer ("Owner", "we", "us").

By adding or using the Bot in any Discord server, you agree to these Terms.

1. Acceptance of Terms

By inviting or interacting with TailWord, you agree to comply with these Terms and Discord’s Terms of Service and Community Guidelines.

If you do not agree, you must remove or stop using the Bot.

2. Description of Service

TailWord provides interactive word-chain gameplay and related features within Discord servers, including:

Word-chain game mechanics

Server and global statistics

Save/reward systems

Voting rewards

Leaderboards

Giveaways and events

Other game-related features

Features may change over time.

