The Bot is provided as-is and availability is not guaranteed.

The Owner reserves the right to:

Modify features

Reset game progress

Change rewards or mechanics

Restart or shut down the service

Perform maintenance or updates

without prior notice.

4. Virtual Economy & Rewards

TailWord may include virtual items such as Saves, rewards, or bonuses.

These:

Have no real-world monetary value

Cannot be exchanged for money or goods

Are not refundable or transferable outside the Service

May be reset or modified at any time

